node.text: Never underestimate the power of a dream. So excited to share this with you! Ever since I was a little girl, I dreamed of going to the Olympics. Dreams are so powerful & it’s incredible where they can take us. My dream got me to where I am today. What about yours? Learn more about @Olay and #PowerOfADream at olay.com/dreams #ad

node.text: April is National Child Abuse Prevention month, and I’m proud to be working with @WoodwardCamp, who is committed to prioritizing safety within their camp experience. Woodward and I are working together to advance the camp’s child safety and health & wellness offerings through a number of different initiatives, including Woodward’s recent partnership with Prevent 360°. A collaborative prevention program from @D2Lorg and @mbfchildsafety , Prevent 360° aims to educate and empower campers, staff, coaches, adults and families to prevent abuse. Other than lots of gymnastics, we’ll also provide gardening, yoga, mental health education and other fun activities throughout camp. Visit the link in my bio for more information, and I hope to see you at camp this summer 😊🤍💙

node.text:
Congrats to my best friend @abbeybergman for finishing cancer treatment. You are a warrior! I can’t wait to give you the biggest hug. 

Abbey & I have been friends since we were around 5. We used to do gymnastics together too. This photo was taken when I was saying goodbye to her before her surgery. This was a natural moment (we didn’t know someone snapped a pic) We’ve always been so close & I am the luckiest to have a friend like Abbey. 🤍

Please send Abbey all of the love & support as she continues on her healing journey! Thank you 🤍

I enjoy learning about ways to live a healthier lifestyle & ways to better take care of myself. I want to tell you about a new part of my nightly self-care routine, SmileDirectClub Nighttime AlignersTM. Recently, I learned there are health benefits to straighter teeth. Straighter teeth make it easier to floss, and that keeps gums healthy. I have personally noticed when I smile my mental health improves. I'm excited to start my Smile Journey™ to get a healthier smile. For anyone who also wants to have a healthier smile, I’m passing along a special discount. Just use promo code ALYSMILES for $100 off @SmileDirectClub aligners.

 

Choose healthy. Choose smile. 😁

#health #routine #selfcare #smiledirectpartner #ad
